Zoleka Mandela is amptelik van chemoterapie af, wat sy vir die afgelope paar maande ondergaan het.Sy het op Instagram laat hoor dat haar chemo, n&aacute; 133 dae, &ldquo;permanent gestaak&rdquo; is.Zoleka het vir &lsquo;n tweede keer kanker beveg, toe haar borskanker vroe&euml;r vanjaar teruggekeer het.Alhoewel sy nie meer chemo ontvang nie, sal Zoleka met &lsquo;n hormoonterapie inspuiting voortgaan.Die newe-effek van die inspuiting beteken dat Zoleka net swanger kan raak in vyf tot tien jaar se tyd, omdat swangerskap die herhaling van die kanker sal affekteer.&ldquo;Dit maak my siel seer. Ek probeer dit nog als verwerk. Toe ek die nuus vroe&euml;r vandag ontvang was dit totaal en al onverwags, maar dit kon erger gewees het,&rdquo; het &lsquo;n positiewe Zoleka ges&ecirc;. - timeslive.co.za&nbsp;Day 133, my Chemotherapy treatments have officially been permanently discontinued. Although my White Blood Cell count has increased, it is still below 1 and on 0.76. I will continue with 1 Zoladex injection (hormone therapy) every 3mnths that stops the body from producing Estrogen. I've been put on Femara (a hormone blocker) to treat hormone receptor positive Breast Cancers like mine, this means that Estrogen is responsible for making the Cancer cells in my body grow faster. I can only try for a baby in 5-10yrs - it's riskier to get pregnant as it will effect recurrence of Cancer. This hurts my soul. I'm still digesting it all, receiving the news earlier today was completely unexpected but it could have been worse ... I'm already on the next chapter of my journey and I feel like I haven't quite turned the last page just yet! No! I know how this will end ... I'm the writer of the next chapter of my life ... She lived soberly, happily and pregnantly ever after - and it's not the end because no Cancer will ever silence me!!! #SilenceCancer #KnowYourCancer #NeverTooLateToRewriteYourLifeStory #ZolekaMandelaFoundation #Chemotherapy #GemCisplatin #BreastCancerSurvivor #Recurrence 